key.name: org.pentaho.reporting.engine.classic.core.modules.gui.base.ActionFactory
key.description: Internal Configuration setting. Do not modify.

key.name: org.pentaho.reporting.engine.classic.core.modules.gui.base.LargeIcons
key.description: Defines, whether the toolbar will contain large icons. This is enabled by default.

key.name: org.pentaho.reporting.engine.classic.core.modules.gui.base.MaximumZoom
key.description: Defines the Maximum Zoom allowed in the preview pane. This is a floating point number which represents a percentage (1.0 = 100%). The default value is 20.0 corresponds to 2000%.

key.name: org.pentaho.reporting.engine.classic.core.modules.gui.base.MenuBarAvailable

key.name: org.pentaho.reporting.engine.classic.core.modules.gui.base.MinimumZoom
key.description: Defines the Minimum Zoom allowed in the preview pane. This is a floating point number which represents a percentage (1.0 = 100%). The default value is 0.01 which corresponds to 1%

key.name: org.pentaho.reporting.engine.classic.core.modules.gui.base.Module

key.name: org.pentaho.reporting.engine.classic.core.modules.gui.base.ProgressBarEnabled
key.description: Defines, whether the progress bar should be visible when repaginating the report. The progress bar is not available for the other exports.

key.name: org.pentaho.reporting.engine.classic.core.modules.gui.base.ProgressDialogEnabled
key.description: Defines, whether the progress dialog should be visible when repaginating the report. Whether the dialog is enabled or disabled for the various exports, can be configured in the export modules.
